  "NITROGEN-F": {
   "name": "NITROGEN-F",
   "file": "cs.zil",
   "line": 1242,
   "endLine": 1282,
   "source": "<ROUTINE NITROGEN-F ()\n\t <COND (<VERB? EXAMINE>\n\t\t<TELL\n\"The flask contains a clear, \" 'NITROGEN \" with a thin white mist\nboiling off of it.\" CR>)\n\t       (<VERB? TAKE RUB>\n\t\t<TELL\n\"The liquid is extremely cold. In fact, you burn your finger on it.\" CR>)\n\t       (<VERB? SMELL>\n\t\t<TELL\n\"The liquid has no smell.\" CR>)\n\t       (<VERB? POUR PUT DROP THROW>\n\t\t<REMOVE ,NITROGEN>\n\t\t<DEQUEUE I-NITROGEN-GOES>\n\t\t<QUEUE I-MIST-GOES 2>\n\t\t<COND (<PRSI? ,FLASK>\n\t\t       <TELL ,GOOD-TRICK>)\n\t\t      (<AND ,PRSI\n\t\t\t    <FSET? ,PRSI ,PERSON>\n\t\t\t    <NOT <PRSI? ,ME ,HAND>>>\n\t\t       <SWAP-VERB ,V?ATTACK>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)\n\t\t      (ELSE\n\t\t       <TELL\n\"The freezing liquid pours out\">\n\t\t       <COND (,PRSI\n\t\t\t      <TELL \" onto \" THE ,PRSI>)>\n\t\t       <TELL \", boiling into cold mist almost immediately\">\n\t\t       <COND (,PRSI\n\t\t\t      <COND (<OR <HELD? ,PRSI>\n\t\t\t\t\t <INTRINSIC? ,PRSI>>\n\t\t\t\t     <JIGS-UP\n\", but not before it freezes you as well.\">\n\t\t\t\t     <RFATAL>)\n\t\t\t\t    (<FSET? ,PRSI ,SLIMEBIT>\n\t\t\t\t     <FCLEAR ,PRSI ,SLIMEBIT>)\n\t\t\t\t    (<FSET? ,PRSI ,TAKEBIT>\n\t\t\t\t     <REMOVE ,PRSI>\n\t\t\t\t     <TELL\n\", but \" THE ,PRSI \" freezes and then shatters from the cold\">)>)>\n\t\t       <TELL \".\" CR>)>)>>"
  },
