   "source": "<ROUTINE HAND-POINTS ()\n\t <TELL CR\n\"The hand \">\n\t <COND (<IN? ,RING ,HAND>\n\t\t<TELL\n\"points its mutilated ring finger \" <GETP ,HERE ,P?POINT> \" and \">)>\n\t <TELL \"grips your shoulder tightly.\" CR>>"
