  "V-$SOUND": {
   "name": "V-$SOUND",
   "file": "globals.zil",
   "line": 41,
   "endLine": 57,
   "source": "<ROUTINE V-$SOUND (\"AUX\" X Y)\n\t <SET X <GET ,SOUND-FLAG 1>>\n\t <SET Y <GET ,SOUND-FLAG 0>>\n\t <TELL \"Sound \">\n\t <COND (.Y\n\t\t<KILL-SOUNDS>\n\t\t<COND (<N==? .Y 1> <PUT ,SOUND-FLAG 1 .Y>)\n\t\t      (ELSE <PUT ,SOUND-FLAG 1 0>)>\n\t\t<PUT ,SOUND-FLAG 0 0>\n\t\t<TELL \"off.\" CR>)\n\t       (ELSE\n\t\t<PUT ,SOUND-FLAG 0 1>\n\t\t<COND (.X\n\t\t       %<IFSOUND <SOUNDS </ .X 16>\n\t\t\t\t\t ,S-START\n\t\t\t\t\t <MOD .X 16>>>)>\n\t\t<TELL \"on.\" CR>)>>"
  },
