   "source": "<ROUTINE INTNUM-F ()\n\t <COND (<PRSO? ,INTNUM>\n\t\t<COND (<HERE? ,CS-ELEVATOR-ROOM>\n\t\t       <REDIRECT ,INTNUM ,FLOOR-BUTTON>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)\n\t\t      (<HERE? ,KITCHEN>\n\t\t       <PUT ,P-ADJW 0 ,W?INTNUM>\n\t\t       <REDIRECT ,INTNUM ,CONTROLS>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)\n\t\t      (<VERB? PUSH>\n\t\t       <TELL S \"There's no number \"\"to push here.\" CR>)>)>>"
