  "NOT-HERE-OBJECT-F": {
   "name": "NOT-HERE-OBJECT-F",
   "file": "globals.zil",
   "line": 233,
   "endLine": 277,
   "source": "<ROUTINE NOT-HERE-OBJECT-F (\"AUX\" TBL (PRSO? T) (X <>))\n\t <COND (<AND <PRSO? ,NOT-HERE-OBJECT>\n\t\t     <PRSI? ,NOT-HERE-OBJECT>>\n\t\t<TELL \"Those things aren't here!\" CR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<PRSO? ,NOT-HERE-OBJECT>\n\t\t<SET TBL ,P-PRSO>\n\t\t<COND (<VERB? FOLLOW WAIT-FOR FIND\n\t\t\t      TELL WHAT WHERE WHO>\n\t\t       <SET X T>)>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<SET TBL ,P-PRSI>\n\t\t<COND (<VERB? ASK-ABOUT ASK-FOR TELL-ABOUT>\n\t\t       <SET X T>)>\n\t\t<SET PRSO? <>>)>\n\t <COND (<AND .X <NOT <FIND-NOT-HERE .TBL .PRSO?>>>\n\t\t<COND (<VERB? FOLLOW>\n\t\t       <TELL\n\"I'm afraid that's not possible.\" CR>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)\n\t\t      (<VERB? WAIT-FOR>\n\t\t       <COND (<AND <PRSO? ,RATS>\n\t\t\t\t   <IN-TUNNEL? ,RATS>\n\t\t\t\t   <IN-TUNNEL?>>\n\t\t\t      <TELL \"All in good time...\" CR>\n\t\t\t      <RTRUE>)\n\t\t\t     (ELSE\n\t\t\t      <COND (<PLURAL? ,PRSO>\n\t\t\t\t     <TELL \"They're\">)\n\t\t\t\t    (ELSE\n\t\t\t\t     <TELL \"He's\">)>\n\t\t\t      <TELL \" not expected any time soon.\" CR>\n\t\t\t      <RTRUE>)>)\n\t\t      (<AND <VERB? TELL>\n\t\t\t    <OR <NOT <EQUAL? <LOC ,PRSO>\n\t\t\t\t\t     ,INF-1 ,INF-2 ,INF-3\n\t\t\t\t\t     ,INF-4 ,INF-5>>\n\t\t\t\t<NOT <HERE? ,INF-1 ,INF-2 ,INF-3\n\t\t\t\t\t    ,INF-4 ,INF-5>>>>\n\t\t       ;<CANT-SEE-ANY-HERE .PRSO?>\n\t\t       ;<RTRUE>)\t\n\t\t      (ELSE\n\t\t       <RFALSE>)>)>\n\t ;\"Here is the default 'cant see any' printer\"\n\t <CANT-SEE-ANY-HERE .PRSO?>>"
  },
  "CANT-SEE-ANY-HERE": {
   "name": "CANT-SEE-ANY-HERE",
   "file": "globals.zil",
   "line": 279,
   "endLine": 291,
   "source": "<ROUTINE CANT-SEE-ANY-HERE (PRSO?)\n\t <COND (<WINNER? ,PLAYER>\n\t\t<TELL \"You\">)\n\t       (ELSE\n\t\t<TELL CTHE ,WINNER>)>\n\t <TELL \" can't see any \">\n\t <COND (,P-OFLAG\n\t\t<COND (<PRINT-ADJT ,P-XADJNT>)>\n\t\t<COND (,P-XNAM <PRINTB ,P-XNAM>)>)\n\t       (ELSE\n\t\t<THING-PRINT .PRSO?>)>\n\t <TELL \" here.\" CR>\n\t <END-QUOTE>>"
  },
  "FIND-NOT-HERE": {
   "name": "FIND-NOT-HERE",
   "file": "globals.zil",
   "line": 293,
   "endLine": 311,
   "source": "<ROUTINE FIND-NOT-HERE (TBL PRSO? \"AUX\" M-F OBJ)\n;\"Special-case code goes here. <MOBY-FIND .TBL> returns # of matches. If 1,\nthen P-MOBY-FOUND is it. You can treat the 0 and >1 cases alike or differently.\nAlways return RFALSE (not handled) if you have resolved the problem.\"\n\t<SET M-F <MOBY-FIND .TBL>>\n\t%<DEBUG-CODE\n\t  <COND (,ZDEBUG\n\t\t <TELL \"[Found \" N .M-F \" obj]\" CR>)>>\n\t<COND (<EQUAL? 1 .M-F>\n\t       %<DEBUG-CODE\n\t\t <COND (,ZDEBUG\n\t\t\t<TELL \"[Namely: \" D ,P-MOBY-FOUND \"]\" CR>)>>\n\t       <COND (.PRSO?\n\t\t      <SETG PRSO ,P-MOBY-FOUND>)\n\t\t     (T\n\t\t      <SETG PRSI ,P-MOBY-FOUND>)>\n\t       <RFALSE>)\n\t      (T\n\t       ,NOT-HERE-OBJECT)>>"
  },
